{"tid":1551367,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國人權及民主法內的五大行動","createTime":"2019-09-08T03:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:44:33.000Z","uid":319328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1307509cf91b511612cf9a3870ebcb572539bc9a","tid":1551367,"uid":319328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"美國人權及民主法內的五大行動大約如下：<br />\n1. 國務卿需每年就香港自治向國會提交報告，認證香港可續享其根據香港政策法下獲得的獨特地位<br />\n2. 授權/要求總統把破壞香港基本自由的人認/列出並凍結其在美資產及拒絕入境<br />\n3. 要求總統制定政策保障美國國民及商界利益<br />\n4. 要求商務部長每年就香港有否執行美國就敏感物資出口法規及美國和聯合國制裁向國會提交報告<br />\n5. 確保申請美國簽證者不會因參與支持民主、人權、或法治的和理非遊行遭補而被拒發入境簽證<br />\n<br />\n（原文在<a href=\"https://www.cecc.gov/media-center/press-releases/commissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cecc.gov%2Fmedia-center%2Fpress-releases%2Fcommissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprmlQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=b58dd7c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cecc.gov/media-center/press-releases/commissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a>）"},{"pid":"ae5773e7cd3f3f1ee59badcffd1c939d301e110f","tid":1551367,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHQtaa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHQtaa9.png&h=0ad2cf29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBvQov9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBvQov9.jpg&h=b7e0dfa3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVPaov9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVPaov9.jpg&h=fd56e246&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}